dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.serviceneeds

Interface IDiagEventDebounceTimeBased

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagEventDebounceAlgorithm, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IDiagEventDebounceTimeBased
extends IEntity, IDiagEventDebounceAlgorithm
    IDiagEventDebounceTimeBased: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class represents the ability to indicate that the time-based pre-debounce algorithm shall be used by the Dem for this diagnostic monitor. This is related to set the EcuC choice container DemDebounceAlgorithmClass to DemDebounceTimeBase.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
